messages.messageBody:
Hi All:

Max has been having a hard time going to bed lately and seemed frightened,
yet didn't want to sleep with us. We've discovered that he and Zak want to
share a room. I hope that works out because it seems to be something they
want to do at the moment....Learning to let them go is harder for me than
for them.

Dawn
